    <Text>Located on elegant Wilshire Boulevard, in the heart of Rodeo Drive, the Beverly Hills Plaza Hotel offers a garden oasis of tranquility. Whether your stay is short or long, the intimate size of the hotel and its hospitality is perfect for you.</Text>
